      <title>中国为Stellantis-Leapmotor合资企业开绿灯--消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-gives-green-light-stellantis-leapmotor-joint-venture-sources-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位知情人士透露，拟议的合资企业已获得中国监管机构的批准，该合资企业将允许世界第四大汽车制造商 Stellantis 在中国境外生产和销售零跑汽车的电动汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-gives-green-light-stellantis-leapmotor-joint-venture-sources-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
