    <item>
      <title>东盟和澳大利亚呼吁停止在南海破坏稳定的行动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asean-australia-call-an-end-destabilising-actions-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，澳大利亚和东盟在为期三天的峰会结束时发表联合声明，称所有国家都应避免在南海采取危及争议地区和平、安全与稳定的单方面行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asean-australia-call-an-end-destabilising-actions-south-china-sea-2024-03-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 06:39:37 GMT</pubDate>
